file.name: webgateway.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp4:
      properties:
        json: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp5:
      properties:
        json: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp6:
      properties:
        name: {type: string}
        title: {type: string}
        type: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth: {scheme: basic, type: http}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of McAfee WebGateway
  title: McAfee WebGateway
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Add an entry to a list within McAfee Webgateway
      parameters:
      - description: The list id of the list to add to
        example: com.scur.type.regex.1704
        in: query
        name: List ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Regex or Name of Entry
        example: google.com
        in: query
        name: Entry Data
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Description of why this entry exists
        example: Nobody uses this site anyways
        in: query
        name: Entry Description
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Commit the changes upon successfully adding to the list
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Commit on Success
        required: true
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200': {description: Successful request}
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Add to List
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Add an entry to an extended list within McAfee Webgateway
      parameters:
      - description: The list id of the extended list to add to
        example: com.scur.type.regex.1704
        in: query
        name: List ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Regex or Name of Entry
        example: google.com
        in: query
        name: Entry Data
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Description of why this entry exists
        example: Nobody uses this site anyways
        in: query
        name: Entry Description
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Commit the changes upon successfully adding to the list
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Commit on Success
        required: true
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200': {description: Successful request}
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Add to Extended List
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Commit changes to McAfee Webgateway
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200': {description: Successful request}
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Commit
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: Remove an entry to a list in McAfee Webgateway
      parameters:
      - description: The list id of the list to add to
        example: com.scur.type.regex.1704
        in: query
        name: List ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Regex or Name of Entry
        example: google.com
        in: query
        name: Entry Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Commit the changes upon successfully deleting the entry from
          the list
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Commit on Success
        required: true
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200': {description: Successful request}
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Delete from List
  tmp4:
    post:
      description: Get entry from list in McAfee Webgateway
      parameters:
      - description: The list id of the list to add to
        example: com.scur.type.regex.1704
        in: query
        name: List ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Regex or Name of Entry
        example: google.com
        in: query
        name: Entry Data
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: ID of entry to search for.
        example: '12'
        in: query
        name: Entry ID
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp4'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Get Entry from List
  tmp5:
    post:
      description: Get list data from McAfee Webgateway
      parameters:
      - description: The list id of the list to add to
        example: com.scur.type.regex.1704
        in: query
        name: List ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp5'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Get List
  tmp6:
    post:
      description: Get all lists with descriptions that can be modified on McAfee
        Webgateway
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp6'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: McAfee Webgateway Get All Lists
tags:
- {name: Network Security & Management}
